{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation and completion"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"handler."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"tex